Package frc.robot

package frc.robot
  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    Constants
    The Constants class provides a convenient place for teams to hold robot-wide numerical or boolean constants.
    Constants.Climber
    Climber motors for Talon SRX's controlling the Climber.
    Constants.DriveTrain
    Drive Train Motor CAN ID's which are used in the Drive Train Subsystem
    Constants.HoodPneumatics
    Hood pneumatics on the CTRE PCM.
    Constants.IntakePneumatics
    Intake Pnuematics channels on the CTRE PCM.
    Main
    Do NOT add any static variables to this class, or any initialization at all.
    Robot
    The VM is configured to automatically run this class, and to call the methods corresponding to each mode, as described in the TimedRobot documentation.
    RobotContainer
    This class is where the bulk of the robot should be declared.
